<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
<head>
    <!-- $title = Careers Single Page -->
    <!-- @include assets/meta-head.kit -->
</head>
<body>


<!-- @include assets/header.kit -->


<!-- ========= Hero Section ========= -->
<section class="hero-section after-header" style="height: 500px;" data-disable-resize>
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="background image" style="background-image: url('images/big-backgrounds/bg4.jpg');" data-parallax="-0.5"></div>

    <!-- Section content -->
    <div class="content remove-padding"><div class="content-inner">
        <h1 class="bold">Careers</h1>
    </div></div>
</section>


<!-- ========= Text section ========= -->
<section class="container big-padding careers-single"><div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9">
        <h1 class="title">Frontend Web Designer <small>Chisinau</small></h1>

        <p>Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor</p>

        <h3>Essential Skills:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Strong front-end skills in HTML5, CSS3 & jQuery</li>
            <li>Experience in responsive/adaptive design techniques</li>
            <li>Make designs real by implementing rich interactions and animations using CSS3 & jQuery</li>
            <li>Experience in implementing Backbone.JS, PHP and AJAX</li>
            <li>Experience with CSS pre-processors (LESS/SASS)</li>
            <li>Experience in version controlling whilst working with other developers</li>
            <li>Experience with version control (especially Git)</li>
            <li>Knowledge of cross-platform and cross-browser issues</li>
            <li>The ability to multitask on several projects whilst working to tight timescales</li>
            <li>High level of self-management and organizational skills</li>
            <li>Knowledge of search engine optimisation</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-3 buttons-col">
        <p><a class="btn btn-default text-uppercase" href="contact.html">Apply</a></p>

        <span class="headings-color">Share on:</span>
        <div class="social-likes social-likes_vertical" data-counters="no" data-single-title="Share">
            <div class="facebook" title="Share link on Facebook">Facebook</div>
            <div class="twitter" title="Share link on Twitter">Twitter</div>
            <div class="plusone" title="Share link on Google+">Google+</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div></section>


<!-- @include assets/footer.kit -->


</body>
</html>